It's a Buster Call!

103
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,830
Battleships are coming!

104
00:09:25,350 --> 00:09:28,750
Hurry up, or we'll be burned to a crisp!

105
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,880
Get out of here!

106
